strings.Value: "I'm sorry, I don't like that. Let's stick to regular love play, ok?"
"Are you sure? I wouldn't want to hurt you..."
"Be careful what you wish for. Next time you won't be able to sit!"
"I've never done that... But if you want to — let's try."
{n}Regongar gets dressed, taking his time.{/n} "You're a miracle. But you know... Next time you don't have to be so tender with me!"

"Don't be afraid to hurt me. Pain is a caress too... When done by someone you love." {n}The half-orc gives you a smile you've never seen before — warm, without a shade of his usual anger or bravado.{/n}
"As you wish. All that matters is your hands on my body... I'll accept anything you give me."
"Oh, you'd have to try hard for that!"
"Don't be afraid! You have no idea what I can stand... And beg for more, haha!"
"Keep saying that, and I'll conquer all the neighboring kingdoms for you."
"I'll teach you. I'm sure you'll love it!"
{n}Regongar is playing with the buckle of his belt.{/n} "Did I get dressed too soon? Want to do it again?"
"Ha ha ha, I'm reading your thoughts!" {n}The half-orc unbuckles his belt.{/n} "Come here..."
"Fine. Come back once you've gathered your strength... You'll need it! I'll be waiting."
